result.name: Café de Coral

reviews.text: First time trying this recipe in cafe de coral! It was a lot of smoke at the beginning when I removed the lid. I had to apologize to the couple next to me because they were in a cloud of smoke because of my food. They react nice, like it was nothing. I felt relieved xd and I started to enjoy this healthy version with pumpkin and pork ribs. So crunchy the toasted rice. Very good combination with pumpkin, even it had the skin on, it was easy to eat. I miss maybe adding one more ingredient. Just the meat, pumpkin and soy sauce is perfect but maybe one more veggie would make it awesome. Nevermind, quite happy to come here sometimes!

result.name: 大家樂

reviews.text: 我已經不止一次在這間大家樂體驗未煮熟食物。今次的早餐肉丸未全熟，已經同餐廳反映，希望會改善。正確煮熟的食品是沒問題的。另外，店員時常會落錯單，食客們要注意。
早餐選擇尚多，份量則不多
大家樂早，午，晚餐，價錢適中，燒腩仔飯，譽香雞飯好食，環境舒適，顯示牌攞食物非常清晰，值得好去處的地方。
食物一般，員工多沒禮貌

大家樂 心胸狹窄 wifi取用不接地氣極困難不便 如果有中源地產在附近
就上了中源 還有大快活提供長者卡難道儂還不知唄
